{"tid":864552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣交會受影響　拒透露美商人數","createTime":"2018-10-16T09:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T13:20:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"556b6937f029fe2344a6a9f8f6e09dcd92bca480","tid":864552,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T09:41:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181016/20523207\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181016%2F20523207&d=19R18GhNToue5Ck1nXThuzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=736122c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181016%2F20523207&h=cb7b20be\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181016/20523207</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月16日 <br />\n<br />\n廣交會受影響　拒透露美商人數<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181016/large/16ck3p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181016%2Flarge%2F16ck3p.jpg&h=df74d905&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中美貿易戰的影響目前尚未浮面，圖為繁忙的上海洋山深水港碼頭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中美貿易戰如火如荼、兩國政治經濟形勢波譎雲詭之際，第124屆中國進出口商品交易會（又稱廣交會）昨日在廣州揭幕。外界關注與會的美國和西方商人數和規模變化，但官方無透露，只稱參展人數與往屆保持基本穩定，但承認貿易戰對交易會有影響。<br />\n<br />\n廣東作為中國經濟大省，對內地經濟和改革開放舉足輕重。隨着中美貿易戰加劇，廣東必然首當其衝，而其應對措施也頗受外界關注。當地媒體報道，因應中美經貿磨擦等因素，廣東相繼推出「實體經濟十條」等政策，以圖穩定外貿發展，優化營商環境，提振企業信心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外貿風向標受關注<br />\n<br />\n作為中國外貿風向標的廣州交易會，有媒體對於美國採購商到場情況表示關注。在14日的記者會上，廣交會新聞發言人徐兵坦言：「國際經濟貿易領域仍然存在一些不確定、不穩定因素，特別是中美經貿磨擦對中國外貿發展造成了一定影響。」<br />\n<br />\n他僅與第122屆人數做比較，稱預計本屆廣交會到會採購商人數，同第122屆「保持基本穩定」，言下之意或難達到第123屆廣交會到會11,929人水平；他續指，多數美國採購商表示將繼續與會參觀採購，但也有部份機構擔心美國貿易政策可能影響採購商的與會積極性。<br />\n<br />\n美國是廣交會的第二大採購商來源地，近年來每屆到會人數均超過1萬人。<br />\n《南方日報》/中央社  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n「中國問題頭號權威」特朗普推崇<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n中共紅色歌劇《洪湖赤衞隊》登陸澳洲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「中國問題頭號權威」特朗普推崇<br />\n<br />\n前白宮智囊下月習特會前放風　華若購1.56萬億美貨　特朗普或「停戰」"},{"pid":"0f090ee7924bb29d19a261bfc07bb2051ab741e1","tid":864552,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T09:41:59.000Z","msg":"廣交會，邊個白痴諗個名出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2de0b0ed7846d7d65acf95d91d1ff46b3dab38","tid":864552,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f090ee7924bb29d19a261bfc07bb2051ab741e1","tid":864552,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T09:41:59.000Z","msg":"廣交會，邊個白痴諗個名出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:30:18.000Z","msg":"廣州交易會。有乜問題？簡稱核突?"},{"pid":"bfec4f469880fa5a405069b840f5826b924e51bd","tid":864552,"uid":20390,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"eb2de0b0ed7846d7d65acf95d91d1ff46b3dab38","tid":864552,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f090ee7924bb29d19a261bfc07bb2051ab741e1","tid":864552,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T09:41:59.000Z","msg":"廣交會，邊個白痴諗個名出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:30:18.000Z","msg":"廣州交易會。有乜問題？簡稱核突?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T13:06:58.000Z","msg":"Child登只會focus呢啲位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614add321c46d20bd817fcf1b3a43428d48d72a6","tid":864552,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score